MAD is full of Sith in its special section on Star Wars: Revenge of the Sith, while its skewering of Batman Begins, er, begins! MAD also tosses high heat at the new D.C. baseball team, threatens the cast of FOX's 24 with time-sensitive questions, and predicts the lousy future of NBC's Medium!
